This release contains several bugfixes and new functionality:

- Sales Order prepayment
- Audit log for financial transactions
- Sales invoice print form customization
- Support for dropship print forms - Sales Order, Packing List, Sales Invoice
- Shipping and discount fields on sales documents
- Improved user experience in payment documents, in particular an ability to apply payments to sales invoices, and view bill payments for a selected bill
- Improved flexibility for selection of different account types for supporting using credit cards
- Data export feature (Lists / Reports)
- Functionality for 1099-MISC reporting
